---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Container from '@/components/ui/Container.astro';
import PageHero from '@/components/blocks/PageHero.astro';
---
<PageLayout title="Terms & Conditions" description="House of Delray terms and conditions of use.">
  <PageHero title="Terms & Conditions" height="none" />

  <section class="legal">
    <Container width="narrow">
      <div class="prose">
        <p class="legal__updated">Last updated: April 1, 2027</p>

        <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing and using the House of Delray website and services, you agree to be bound by these
          Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website
          or services.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Reservations & Booking</h2>
        <p>
          All reservations are subject to availability. By making a reservation, you agree to the specific
          rate, cancellation policy, and terms associated with the booking package selected. A valid credit
          card is required to guarantee your reservation.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Check-In & Check-Out</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Check-in time: 3:00 PM</li>
          <li>Check-out time: 11:00 AM</li>
          <li>Early check-in and late check-out are subject to availability and may incur additional charges.</li>
          <li>Valid government-issued photo identification is required at check-in.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Cancellation Policy</h2>
        <p>
          Cancellation policies vary by rate type and package. Please refer to your booking confirmation
          for specific cancellation terms. In general:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Standard rates: Free cancellation up to 48 hours before check-in.</li>
          <li>Non-refundable rates: No cancellation or modification permitted.</li>
          <li>Special packages: Subject to individual package terms.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Property Rules</h2>
        <p>Guests are expected to respect the property and other guests. The following rules apply:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Smoking is not permitted indoors.</li>
          <li>Quiet hours are observed between 11:00 PM and 7:00 AM.</li>
          <li>Pets are not permitted unless prior arrangements have been made.</li>
          <li>Guests are responsible for any damage caused to the property during their stay.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Liability</h2>
        <p>
          House of Delray shall not be liable for any loss, damage, or injury to guests or their property,
          except where caused by our negligence. We recommend that guests secure valuable items in the
          in-room safe provided.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          All content on this website — including text, images, logos, and design elements — is the
          property of House of Delray and is protected by copyright and trademark laws. You may not
          reproduce, distribute, or use any content without our prior written consent.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Your use of our website is also governed by our
          <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>. Please review it to understand how we collect
          and use your information.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms & Conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the
          State of Israel. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts
          of Tel Aviv-Jaffa.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For questions about these Terms & Conditions, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>House of Delray</strong><br />
          8 Nes HaGalshan St.<br />
          Kerem HaTeimanim, Tel Aviv<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:info@delray.com">info@delray.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    padding: var(--section-padding-y) 0;
  }

  .legal__updated {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-warm-gray);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
</style>
